Class BaseSet<Value>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.BaseCollection<Value>
com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.set.BaseSet<Value>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Countable, Addable<Value>, Copyable<Value,BaseSet<Value>>, Emptiness, Joinable<Value>, Sequence<Value>, Sized, SpaceLimited, Factory<BaseSet<Value>>, Zeroable, AsString, StringFormattable, Iterable<Value>, Collection<Value>, Set<Value>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConcurrentHashSet, IdentitySet, ObjectSet
public abstract class BaseSet<Value> extends BaseCollection<Value> implements Copyable<Value,BaseSet<Value>>, Set<Value>
A set with a maximum size. Adds useful methods to the usual Set operations, as well as implementing:
  • Set
  • Sequence
  • Addable
  • Copyable
  • Countable
  • Joinable
  • StringFormattable
